        "heroTitle": "Department of Electronics &amp; Communication Engineering",
        "aboutHtml": "<p class=\"n-label\">About</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"n-heading\" style=\"font-size:1.5rem;\">Department Overview</h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"n-divider\"></div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify; color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.8;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe Department of Electronics and Communication Engineering (ECE) was established\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tin <strong>1980</strong> and has since met the growing demands of industry and\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsociety. The department has seven Ph.D. holders, and many faculty members are\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tpursuing their Ph.D. in various areas of ECE. The department has an undergraduate\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tintake of <strong>240 students</strong>. The postgraduate programme with a\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tspecialisation in <strong>VLSI System Design</strong> was started in 2025 with\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tan intake of 18 students.\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify; color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.8; margin-top:12px;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe B.Tech programme in ECE was accredited by NBA for the\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<strong>fourth time under Tier-I</strong> for three years. The NBA Expert Team\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tvisited the campus during 11–13 November 2016 and evaluated five departments —\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tECE, EEE, CSE, Civil, and Mechanical Engineering — under Tier-I System. All five\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdepartments were accredited for 2016–17, 2017–18, and 2018–19 up to 30-06-2019.\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify; color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.8; margin-top:12px;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe department is identified as a <strong>Research Centre by JNTUA</strong> to\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tpursue Ph.D programmes. It has a professional association that conducts the\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tnational-level technical symposium <strong>AXION</strong> every year. Students\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tare encouraged to design and develop hardware projects, and IEEE, IE, CSI, and\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIETE institutional chapters conduct regular student events for imparting knowledge\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tand technical skills.\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify; color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.8; margin-top:12px;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tECE students are active in the Literary Club, Painting Club, and Cultural Club,\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tand participate in social service events through platforms like EYE CROSS\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFoundation and Helping Hands. Regular workshops and conferences are conducted to\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tmotivate students towards research activities.\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify; color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.8; margin-top:12px;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe department houses <strong>11 fully-equipped laboratories</strong>: Electronic\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCircuits Lab, Analog &amp; Digital Communication Lab, Microprocessor Lab, Digital\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tSignal Processing Lab, Integrated Circuits Applications Lab, Pulse &amp; Digital\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCircuits Lab, Electronic Design &amp; Automation Lab, Simulation Lab, Hardware\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tLaboratory, Embedded Systems &amp; IoT Lab, and VLSI Lab.\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"n-dept-content-block\" style=\"margin-top:28px;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"n-label\">Academics</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"n-heading\" style=\"font-size:1.4rem;\">Programs Offered</h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"n-divider\"></div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"table-responsive\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<table class=\"n-dept-table\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<thead>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>S.No</th>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>Course</th>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>Branch / Specialisation</th>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>Intake</th>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</thead>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>B.Tech</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Electronics &amp; Communication Engineering</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td><span class=\"n-badge-intake\">240</span></td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>2</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>M.Tech</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>VLSI System Design</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td><span class=\"n-badge-intake\">18</span></td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
