        "aboutHtml": "<p class=\"n-label\">About</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"n-heading\" style=\"font-size:1.5rem;\">Department Overview</h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"n-divider\"></div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify; color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.8;\">\r\n\tThe Mechanical Engineering Department was established in <strong>1979</strong>. The department has an intake of <strong>60 undergraduate</strong> and <strong>18 postgraduate</strong> students. The B.Tech Programme in Mechanical Engineering offered by the Department has been accredited by NBA for the fourth time under Tier-I for three years.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.8; margin-top:12px;\">\r\n\tThe department is recognized as a research centre by JNTUA, Ananthapuramu. The department is funded by various government bodies and supported by industries with grants from DST, AICTE, AR&DB. The department has a good number of MOU’s with manufacturing and automotive domains. Industrial training and bridge courses are conducted periodically.\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; color:var(--text-muted); line-height:1.8; margin-top:12px;\">\r\n\tThe hands-on training is offered by our 3D Experience platform laboratory through EDS Technologies & Dassault systems supported by APSSDC, VI laboratory, and Aveva centre of excellence on DDMS. The department is equipped with <strong>ten laboratories</strong>, a very big central workshop, and research laboratories. Robotics lab is established in association with E-Yantra Project IIT Bombay under MHRD-NMICT.\r\n</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"n-dept-content-block\" style=\"margin-top:28px;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"n-label\">Academics</p>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"n-heading\" style=\"font-size:1.4rem;\">Programs Offered</h2>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"n-divider\"></div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"table-responsive\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<table class=\"n-dept-table\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<thead>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>S.No</th>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>Course</th>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>Branch / Specialisation</th>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>Intake</th>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</thead>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>1</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>B.Tech</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Mechanical Engineering</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td><span class=\"n-badge-intake\">60</span></td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>2</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>M.Tech</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>Robotics &amp; AI</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td><span class=\"n-badge-intake\">18</span></td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
